title: 820-3435 shorted
message:
Hello, I need help with 820-3435 board. it has shorted to ground voltage: PPBUS_S5_HS_COMPUTING_ISNS.

How to solve short, do I need solder one by one all caps in that circuit? (they all looks intact)

title: 820-3435 shorted
message: Inject voltage on the rail and see what heats up. Slowly go up in voltage and monitor current. At 2-3 amps something should get warm. Don't go over 12V of course!
